&lt;h1&gt;DTC GROWTH STRATEGIST&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A DTC Growth Strategist at CTC drives profitable growth for clients by translating raw financial data into precise marketing maneuvers. You will guide clients and teammates with clear financial models, diagnostic reviews, and actionable recommendations, ensuring every marketing dollar is understood through the lens of profit.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;When results deviate from plan, you’ll take ownership in diagnosing the issue, adjusting forecasts, and optimizing within the meta account in order to restore profitable growth. Above all, you are the financial steward of your accounts—trusted to bring clarity, accuracy, and solutions that align business goals with sustainable outcomes.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE LOOK FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This place isn’t for everyone, but it might be for you if…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU SET THE STANDARD&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You seek to define “best in class” across both growth strategy and media buying.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You arrive prepared with forecasts, insights, and clear next steps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You approach challenge and failure with curiosity and resilience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your word is trustworthy — people know that if you are involved, it will get done.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your word is trustworthy; you do what you say you will&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU ARE DRIVEN TO INCREASE VALUE&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You exist to turn marketing strategies into financial outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re excited by the complexities of a business and love identifying growth solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive at translating platform execution into contribution margin and growth targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You clearly articulate complex concepts in ways that clients and teammates can understand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are in the habit of documenting, reporting, and forecasting your work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU CREATE AN ENVIRONMENT OF EXCELLENCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You inspire others with your expertise and strategic thinking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You proactively share insights with your team and clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You embody humility (willing to do the work), ambition (vision for the future), and empathy (understanding what drives others).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You contribute learnings back into CTC’s systems and playbooks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You balance strategy, execution, and communication to help others thrive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STRATEGY &amp;amp; FORECASTING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain growth forecasts in Statlas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align forecasts with marketing calendars, launches, and contribution margin goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate forecasts into daily/weekly pacing to ensure spend and performance remain within targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEDIA EXECUTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, manage, and optimize campaigns across Meta, wile overseeing the management of Google, and YouTube (with expansion to TikTok, Pinterest, Snapchat).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead creative diversification and media testing to profitably scale accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and interpret incrementality tests (geo holdouts, conversion lift) and integrate results into iROAS modeling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot campaigns quickly and pivot strategies when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifecycle &amp;amp; Retention Strategist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Direct-to-consumer marketing success requires mastery of owned channels. We believe that email and SMS marketing are cornerstone channels for sustainable growth. As a Lifecycle &amp;amp; Retention Marketing Strategist, you&#39;ll play a key role in creating education and best practices for our teams, auditing new and existing clients, creating roadmaps for automated campaigns and flows, and providing strategic input across client accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role demands both visionary strategy and flawless execution. You&#39;ll craft data-driven lifecycle strategies while building the technical infrastructure and detailed implementation roadmaps that turn strategy into measurable results for our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Look For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This place isn&#39;t for everyone, but it might be for you if…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU SET THE STANDARD&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are committed to making decisions informed by research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your customer service is referenced as the bar that others strive to emulate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take pride in arriving to meetings prepared with insight to contribute&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You organize your time and say “no” appropriately so that you can attend to what is most critical&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are committed to approaching challenge &amp;amp; failure with curiosity about how to improve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your word is trustworthy; you do what you say you will&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU ARE DRIVEN TO INCREASE VALUE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are passionate about building brands for the next generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You gather context ahead of meetings so that you arrive prepared with insight and input&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You clearly articulate your expertise so that even a beginner can understand the concept&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are in the habit of documenting and reporting your work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOU CREATE AN ENVIRONMENT OF EXCELLENCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You seek opportunities to refine your skills without being prompted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You desire to inspire others with your excellence and expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are willing to put in the reps to be an expert in your domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You resist the temptation to play victim; instead, you take 100% ownership over outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EXECUTE&lt;/strong&gt; | You are hands-on in managing the day-to-day email and SMS programs for your clients. From building complex automation flows and developing sophisticated segmentation strategies to writing compelling copy and setting up A/B tests, you&#39;re comfortable getting into the technical details. You maintain rigorous QA processes, monitor deliverability metrics, and continuously optimize campaign performance. Your expertise in ESPs (especially Klaviyo) allows you to build and manage scalable, revenue-driving programs that consistently exceed client expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TEACH&lt;/strong&gt; | You&#39;re all about creating unique and differentiated customer experiences through email and SMS that drive engagement and revenue. You understand that these channels are key to successful business growth - for both the client and our agency. As an Email &amp;amp; SMS Marketing Strategist, you are building your expertise in all things email and SMS at the agency. The best part of amassing all this knowledge and expertise is that you&#39;ll get to share it with your colleagues and clients as you teach best practices and share foundational knowledge of ESP platforms, automation strategies,

&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SENIOR PAID MEDIA STRATEGIST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROLE OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A Senior Paid Media Strategist at CTC is a full-funnel expert across both paid search and paid social. You operate as the lead media strategist for your client portfolio, combining deep Paid Media mastery to drive outcomes across the entire paid media ecosystem. You analyze data, develop strategy, execute with precision, and communicate results with clarity. You elevate everyone around you.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
