&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You seek opportunities to sharpen your skills without being prompted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You resist the temptation to play victim; you own outcomes 100%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re willing to put in the reps to be a domain expert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You inspire others through the standard you hold for yourself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INNOVATE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You stay on the frontier of paid media strategy and technology across both search and social. You combine data analysis and client feedback to develop strategic plans spanning Google Ads and Meta. You make tactical recommendations for targeting, messaging, and campaign optimization across platforms. You test constantly, investigate relentlessly, and adapt strategy based on statistical outcomes. When it&#39;s time to pivot, you&#39;re among the first. You bring early insights to the team and lead the way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CREATE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Creative problems take creative solutions. You write compelling direct-response copy for both search and social, build out campaigns in Google Ads and Meta Ads Manager, and ensure every initiative is launched on time, on budget, and built to win. You use historical data to guide decisions and find the hidden solution others miss. Attention to detail, proactive problem-solving, and data-driven decision-making are non-negotiables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OWN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;KPIs are your bread and butter. Google Sheets is your jam. &quot;Count on Me&quot; is your mantra. You see things through to the end. You project monthly budgets for each account, back every recommendation with data, and communicate results clearly to clients and teammates. You hold yourself to a high standard and share your learnings to elevate the buyers around you. People know: if you&#39;re involved, it gets done

